fields.Title: JAM / RACIST CABIN
fields.Description: You can view the racist lorryman's cabin to get a load of his racist paraphernalia.

fields.Title: You: "Look in the window."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look in the window.

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "A large metal pendant hangs from th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A large metal pendant hangs from the rear view mirror. The pendant features a sun crowned with wavy rays.

fields.Title: Encyclopedia: "It is the seal of Royalist-era Reva..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It is the seal of Royalist-era Revachol.

fields.Title: Half Light: "He was acting tough before. This de..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He was acting tough before. This definitely scared him a little, you being here.

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Graad Factory of Magnets and Miracles U49: "It's clear this is your guy. Only t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's clear this is your guy. Only the March edition of 'Power Man Monthly: The Pure Man's Magazine' is missing. It's clearly the rotund raceman's.

fields.Title: You: "What kind of stickers and insignia?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What kind of stickers and insignia?

fields.Title: You: "What about the back seat?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What about the back seat?

fields.Title: You: "Look for a clue about who drives th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Look for a clue about who drives the vehicle.

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["jam.truckman_greeting_done"] == false  and  IsKimHere() == false  and  Variable["jam.truckman_cabin_back_end"] == true

fields.Title: Graad Factory of Magnets and Miracles U49: "A lorry stuck in the traffic jam. T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A lorry stuck in the traffic jam. This big, heavy Graad-made machine is well kept for such an old machine.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Racist-nationalist paraphernalia."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Racist-nationalist paraphernalia." He grits his teeth. "Not unusual in this part of town."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Racist-nationalist paraphernalia."..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Racist-nationalist paraphernalia." He grits his teeth. "Not unusual in this part of town. This is our guy." The lieutenant nods towards the racist lorry driver.

fields.Title: Graad Factory of Magnets and Miracles U49: "The driver has adorned his space wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The driver has adorned his space with a substantial collection of peculiar paraphernalia. Proclamations about *honour*, *strength*, and *purity* are glued to various panels.
fields.Alternate1: The driver has adorned the side walls with a substantial collection of racist paraphernalia. Proclamations about *honour*, *strength*, and *purity* are glued to various panels.

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "A book with ragged edges catches yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A book with ragged edges catches your notice. The front cover features a large, muscular man. The title reads: 'Man from Hjelmdall in the Lost City of the Pygmies'.

fields.Title: Perception (Smell): "Fumes of heavy fuel oil waft over y..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fumes of heavy fuel oil waft over you, making your eyes sting. The odour mixes with cigarette residue.

fields.Title: Half Light: "He was acting tough before. This pr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He was acting tough before. This probably scared him a bit. Who knows when it will come in handy -- a slightly scared racist lorryman?

fields.Title: You: ""You think this lorry belongs to ou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You think this lorry belongs to our tough guy?"

dialogueEntries.conditionsString: Variable["jam.truckman_greeting_done"] == true  and  IsKimHere()  and  Variable["jam.truckman_cabin_back_end"] == true

fields.Title: Composure: "There he is, in front of Frittte, s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There he is, in front of Frittte, smoking nervously. Hoping it's over.

fields.Title: Perception (Sight): "The back end of the cabin has a sma..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The back end of the cabin has a small perch to sleep. Large ashtrays. There are several suns and wheels sown into the curtains.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Likely, yes. This guy's proud of w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Likely, yes. This guy's proud of who he is. Drapes it all over his machine."

fields.Title: Graad Factory of Magnets and Miracles U49: "The windows are clear, they've been..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The windows are clear, they've been recently washed. You can see a lorryman's cabin with personal belongings, stickers, insignia...

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]
